---
layout: layouts/element.njk
title: "main"
description: "The dominant content of the document body. Contains the primary content unique to the page, excluding headers, footers, navigation, and sidebars."
elementName: main
category: native
nativeGroup: Sectioning
currentPath: /docs/elements/native/main/
permalink: /docs/elements/native/main/
---

{% set defaultCode %}<header class="site">
  <strong>Site</strong>
</header>
<main>
  <h2>Page Content</h2>
  <p>This is the main content area of the page.</p>
</main>
<footer class="minimal">
  <p>Site Footer</p>
</footer>{% endset %}

{% set containedCode %}<main class="contained">
  <h2>Contained Layout</h2>
  <p>Content is contained to a comfortable reading
  width (1200px) and centered on the page.</p>
</main>{% endset %}

{% set narrowCode %}<main class="narrow">
  <h2>Narrow Layout</h2>
  <p>Ideal for long-form reading content like blog
  posts and documentation, keeping line lengths
  comfortable at 65ch max-width.</p>
</main>{% endset %}

{% set wideCode %}<main class="wide">
  <h2>Wide Layout</h2>
  <p>More horizontal space for complex interfaces,
  data tables, and dashboards at 1600px max-width.</p>
</main>{% endset %}

{% set fullCode %}<main class="full">
  <p>Full-width layout spans the entire viewport
  with consistent padding.</p>
</main>{% endset %}

{% set sidebarCode %}<main class="with-sidebar">
  <article>
    <h2>Main Content</h2>
    <p>Primary content area that takes up the
    majority of the space.</p>
  </article>
  <aside class="sidebar">
    <h4>Sidebar</h4>
    <p>Secondary content or navigation.</p>
  </aside>
</main>{% endset %}

{% set paddedCode %}<main class="padded contained">
  <p>Padded main has generous vertical spacing,
  useful when the parent container does not
  provide padding.</p>
</main>{% endset %}

{% set fullPageCode %}<header class="site">
  <strong>Site</strong>
  <nav class="horizontal pills">
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</header>
<main class="contained padded">
  <h2>Page Title</h2>
  <p>Page content with proper semantic structure.</p>
</main>
<footer class="minimal">
  <p>Footer content</p>
</footer>{% endset %}

  <section>
    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <p>Use the <code>&lt;main&gt;</code> element for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The primary content area of a page</li>
      <li>Content that is unique to this specific page</li>
      <li>The target for skip links ("Skip to main content")</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Important: There should only be one visible <code>&lt;main&gt;</code> element per page. If using multiple for SPA views, only one should be visible at a time (hide others with <code>hidden</code> attribute).</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Examples</h2>

    <h3>Default</h3>
    <p>Basic main element within a page structure.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/main-default.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/main/default" title="Default main" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Default main">{{ defaultCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.contained</h3>
    <p>Centered with max-width of 1200px.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/main-contained.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/main/contained" title="Contained main" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Contained main">{{ containedCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.narrow</h3>
    <p>Optimized for reading content (65ch max-width).</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/main-narrow.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/main/narrow" title="Narrow main" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Narrow main">{{ narrowCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.wide</h3>
    <p>Expanded width (1600px) for dashboards and data-heavy layouts.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/main-wide.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/main/wide" title="Wide main" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Wide main">{{ wideCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.full</h3>
    <p>Full viewport width with side padding.</p>
    <code-block language="html" label="Full-width main">{{ fullCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.with-sidebar</h3>
    <p>Two-column layout with sidebar.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/main-with-sidebar.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/main/sidebar" title="Main with sidebar" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Main with sidebar">{{ sidebarCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.padded</h3>
    <p>Adds vertical padding for spacing. Combine with other variants.</p>
    <code-block language="html" label="Padded main">{{ paddedCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>Full page structure</h3>
    <p>Complete page layout example.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/main-full-page.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/main/full-page" title="Full page layout" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Full page layout">{{ fullPageCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Variants</h2>
    <table class="props-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Class</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><code>.contained</code></td>
          <td>Max-width 1200px, centered with horizontal padding</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>.narrow</code></td>
          <td>Max-width 65ch for comfortable reading</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
